jobs.desc:
- Participation in the development team of a mobile application for conflict management using GIS technology;
- Responsible for front-end architecture, implementation of new features, versioning, and sprint deliveries;
- Collaboration with other development teams to ensure UX/UI consistency and high-quality deliveries;
- Maintenance, optimization, and evolution of the main application;

- Active participation in the development and evolution of a YMS web application using Laravel and Vue, delivering continuous improvements in usability, performance, and scalability;
- Implementation and development of an Android application with React Native/Expo, integrating native features and expanding and improving application quality;
- Delivery of high-impact features aligned with best practices in user experience and software architecture;
- Definition and application of development best practices with the team, including Clean Code, Conventional Commits, and improvements to version control and workflow;

- Development of interactive GIS-focused applications using React, TypeScript, ArcGIS API, and ArcGIS Experience Builder;
- Creation of Python scripts for workflow automation and geospatial data processing;
- Participation in technical consulting for mapping and development of native ArcGIS applications, supporting clients from design to the implementation of GIS solutions;
